{"id":"c7b98c74-2a0e-4560-8797-6310553db193","title":"1512/10","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"17879425-c69e-46bb-85f1-4319bcfd84e2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [October, 1512].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5d913bcf-6ec7-493a-9fd1-3f9bdde8c07d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e63b8505-a87b-4b89-894c-48893dafcd74","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":24,"value":"a50aee6a-2e37-47f7-b3db-464eb6ff2e03","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b4cd27bb-ab5b-4b85-95a0-22ac6b754d15","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lodovico di Buonarrota Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"460cdb7f-3998-4da1-ab6f-283593d89dc9","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c400a4ab-da6e-461e-a0a9-c3f7d0c87239","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"442d7ae1-6c8a-41fa-ac06-fe5b6a060553","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"48b54fd7-8689-4e74-9d10-efbc76f1004c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"44cce770-3e68-44e8-8402-d323374689d6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7ddf7776-922b-4299-842e-1df7de6e55ea","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Dearest Father,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0In your last letter you tell me to be careful not to keep money in the house and not to carry any about with me; also that I am reported\u00A0in Florence as having spoken against the Medici.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"46b0016f-7fbe-48cf-91dc-a8a4a6b60481","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":13,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"af636e1a-76e8-4e13-b04d-55459d77e74a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":13,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bd02a9a8-1edf-4e23-8906-df2a6f9b9bae","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":21,"end":24,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"39a49ecf-42f9-4f10-a678-caf20405871f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":38,"end":40,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"07e5d546-0340-4991-8068-f7fd7978b19e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":47,"end":48,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"96b055e6-28b2-4ab2-80e6-a9ef0f0fed61","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":127,"end":128,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"afafe554-3e0e-4241-b82e-7f97fbff47fa","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":141,"end":141,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f637f976-0fef-4316-b2e0-bac753057743","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":158,"end":165,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e11ba8d7-3215-4279-9df4-1d2d53e4e1c2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":196,"end":201,"value":"f58ed5e3-a380-4e53-aa74-f7a8e7e7b3eb","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"bc562b59-20b1-40a6-a79b-7f45f75242cf","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"deb508ec-bc51-4da6-b48b-6850f8839ab7","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"As to the money, all I have lies in Balducci\u0027s bank, and I keep none of it either in the house nor upon my person, except such sums as are necessary from day to day. With regard to the Medici, I have never\u00A0uttered a single word against them except in the general terms in which everybody talks\u00A0\u2014\u00A0as, for instance, about the Prato affair. I think that\u00A0even the very stones would have spoken of it, had they been able. There have been many other things said since then, to which, when I heard them, I have always replied :\u2014\u00A0\u0022If they are really doing these\u00A0things, they are doing wrong.\u0022 Not that I believed the reports, and God grant they be not true. About a month ago someone who pretended to be my friend\u00A0criticised their actions very adversely. I rebuked him, saying that those who spoke in such a way did wrong, and that he was not to mention the subject to\u00A0me again. However, I should like Buonarroto to find out quietly where the man in question heard that I had spoken against the Medici, so that I may endeavour to trace the origin of the rumour, and find out whether it came from someone professing to be my friend. I shall then be upon my guard. I have nothing more to add. As yet I have begun nothing, and I am waiting until the Pope tells me what I am\u00A0to do.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5d38a65d-c5cd-4c8f-8e78-a7d07947b128","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":21,"end":21,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"870a6b3e-7242-4330-b48a-6a4053bc2517","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":36,"end":43,"value":"24535c01-687a-4e00-bb3f-b9b0f446e6ab","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ec99146e-24e5-494f-8eb3-234762039257","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":57,"end":57,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b3512dae-40b7-4431-acfa-d3db1cc74dad","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":104,"end":105,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"27800f0e-2c17-4bd5-9d72-ed992f4f1eb2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":185,"end":190,"value":"f58ed5e3-a380-4e53-aa74-f7a8e7e7b3eb","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0cc2edb8-6430-46f4-84de-4b5322428eee","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":193